metadata.title: Mightyskins Skin Compatible with Hp Chromebook 11.6" (2014) Touchscreen Sticker Skins Leaf Splatter
features: This is not a HARD CASE. It is a vinyl skin/decal sticker and is not made of rubber, silicone, gel or plastic.
description: Mighty Skins are removable vinyl skins for protecting and customizing your portable devices. This is a decal skin that applies to your existing HP Chromebook 11. 6" Touchscreen. They feature Ultra High Resolution designs, The perfect way to add some style and stand out from the crowd. Mighty Skins have a durable laminate that protects from scratching, fading and peeling. With our patented adhesive technology Mighty Skins remove cleanly when you want to remove them or switch to another design. No sticky mess ! Best of all, we include a FREE digital wallpaper download, so the front of your HP Chromebook 11. 6" Touchscreen can look as great as the back. Hip Chromebook 11. 6" Touchscreen is not included.
